text = "How to run your already trained Agent ...

Click on \"run\" and watch it go.  You can also see its intended path by
looking at the output screen below the game animation screen. 
The ideal path for this tutorial version of the game is: 3,2,2,3,2,2,2,2
You will need to modify the training variables in the tester_tutorial 
g script and the rewards given there to get the ideal path. 
Then, to get the ideal path to be follwoed when the Agent runs, you
will likely need to modify the movement parameters in the player code."

